{"tid":801954,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑倫敦金公司公然係科大請人 連登神探入黎睇下發生咩事","createTime":"2018-09-01T05:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T11:28:16.000Z","uid":37863,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"12bb5355c416bdcc68ab01ff7a7a97f7178836a6","tid":801954,"uid":37863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:37:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近岩岩畢業搵緊工，in左間好鬼嘅公司，之前係另一個post都有巴打討論過呢間野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/700873/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/700873/page/1</a><br />\n之後我開始搵資料，點知發現好唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIn個陣有個女人HR，再到個男人in, 個男人所有野都吹到好大，聲稱係間就黎上市嘅MNC, 亦會問好多你嘅個人問題，仲會問你有咩其他offer, 之後係咁踩你份工。到入正題啦，間野到底係做咩嘅呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n間公司叫Galaxy, ，如果搵佢D job ad, 有時會出 <a href=\"http://www.galaxycapital.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.galaxycapital.io&d=SWLYNpYq6C6koax7h%2FOlHv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a58c7af9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.galaxycapital.io</a> 呢個空白網頁，但in完之發先知，原來佢真正做嘅網係叫 <a href=\"http://miex.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmiex.io&d=SWLYNpYq6C6koax7h%2FOlHv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a9eed55f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">miex.io</a> ，就咁click入去已經覺得伏味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/132752_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F132752_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png&h=fac4a39d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<strong>疑點1 好人好姐點解開幾十個名</strong><br />\nGalaxy Consultancy/ Galaxy capital/ Galaxy Advisory Limited其實全部都係同一間公司，個地址都係金鐘<br />\n最重要嘅係，<a href=\"http://佢係所有jobad都唔會話你知佢其實即係miex.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BD%A2%E4%BF%82%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89jobad%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E6%9C%83%E8%A9%B1%E4%BD%A0%E7%9F%A5%E4%BD%A2%E5%85%B6%E5%AF%A6%E5%8D%B3%E4%BF%82miex.io&d=SWLYNpYq6C6koax7h%2FOlHv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=b2e58f67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">佢係所有jobad都唔會話你知佢其實即係miex.io</a>, 如果佢無野點解要閃閃縮縮，連公司唯一嘅product都唔可以話比人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/132940_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F132940_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png&h=6ed3b8c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>疑點2 大公司要租共享office</strong><br />\n有D job ad佢寫自已嘅地址係<br />\n11/F Admiralty Centre Tower 2, 18 Harcourt Road, Admiralty, Hong Kong<br />\n呢個亦都係佢interview嘅地址<br />\n<br />\n但其實佢只係個共享office, 想知邊間MNC要慘到搵間房仔呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.compassoffices.com/zh-hant/locations/hong-kong/admiralty-centre/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.compassoffices.com%2Fzh-hant%2Flocations%2Fhong-kong%2Fadmiralty-centre%2F&d=SWLYNpYq6C6koax7h%2FOlHv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=bf14a86a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.compassoffices.com/zh-hant/locations/hong-kong/admiralty-centre/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>疑點3疑似偷片改logo</strong><br />\n呢張圖會唔會假得有D離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/133128_10fb15c77258a991b0028080a64fb42d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F133128_10fb15c77258a991b0028080a64fb42d.png&h=c29d4bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個更加離譜，都唔知邊度搵條片key自己logo上去(全部係frontpage已經有)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/133032_09dd8c2662b96ce14928333f055c5580.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F133032_09dd8c2662b96ce14928333f055c5580.png&h=90d5a1a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>疑點4 古惑的牌</strong><br />\n到重點啦，間野似乎係做高杆桿交易CFD, 亦有外匯，吹到有世界多國監管，但係佢全部都係野雞國家，牌照號碼一率失奉，最重要嘅英國FCA，澳洲ASIC，香港證監幾個牌都無 (呢度唔熟，求巴打補充)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/133033_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F133033_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png&h=2d95d92c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nClick入媒體報道仲好笑，入面嘅link全部都係講緊crypto, CFD, 係報導緊個行業，完全同間公司無關，佢都可以拎黎打飛機，人唔笑，狗都吠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>疑點5 消失的歷史</strong><br />\n間野聲稱自已有幾百萬客，成立左成10年，但唔知點解聽都未聽過，<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/133221_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F133221_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png&h=efb0ca30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聲稱自已有好多個獎<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/133234_9eb9cd58b9ea5e04c890326b5c1f471f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F133234_9eb9cd58b9ea5e04c890326b5c1f471f.png&h=e3d43bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係根據FDRC 嘅記錄，間野係2018年3月先成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/133249_602e8f042f463dc47ebfdf6a94ed5a6d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F133249_602e8f042f463dc47ebfdf6a94ed5a6d.png&h=fb4ba0d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，如果大家Google百度 wiki都會發現係完全搵唔到呢間公司嘅任何資料，甚至冇人討論過，換言之，間野好大可能係新開嘅倫敦金公司<br />\n<br />\n<strong>疑點6 假車牌</strong><br />\n間野係網頁最底寫自己係大登記左 粤icp备17150476号<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/133257_7afbb1602613ec52b265d7a54ad27330.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F133257_7afbb1602613ec52b265d7a54ad27330.png&h=9dc85fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係上去一check&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"http://gdcainfo.miitbeian.gov.cn/publish/query/indexFirst.action\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgdcainfo.miitbeian.gov.cn%2Fpublish%2Fquery%2FindexFirst.action&d=SWLYNpYq6C6koax7h%2FOlHv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=2af9a452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://gdcainfo.miitbeian.gov.cn/publish/query/indexFirst.action</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/133304_586e508f161f26ce94633729ac56c602.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F133304_586e508f161f26ce94633729ac56c602.png&h=3d9573cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n暫時睇佢頭一版已經發現咁多問題，簡單啲來講，呢間好大可能係香港無牌呃鳩大陸人嘅倫敦金公司，你可能會話，死嘅係蝗蟲有乜所謂，但係佢喺大學聯招搵工網同埋各大專院校網頁瘋狂出post，年終都唔知幾多無辜fg一車車入去中伏，而大學呢，係完全冇審查過公司背景嘅<br />\n<br />\n其實我搵到嘅資料都係好膚淺，有冇巴打有料爆，或者可以睇吓佢domain有冇咩問題<br />\n<br />\n最後，有冇巴打識backup佢D野，廢時mon post刪野<br />\n<br />\n戴定頭盔先，以上全部都係公開資料黎"},{"pid":"2b702ee33d990b1433f0402372fef990e6482a4d","tid":801954,"uid":37863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d58d75901e51f7ae4482921f20447d2e08bf5a","tid":801954,"uid":35536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:46:11.000Z","msg":"屌 真係好撚仆街<br />\n喺jijis瘋狂開post請人<br />\n但又唔知間公司做乜鳩"},{"pid":"f0b3757ad496b2248968ac91dbe1d6f86e9fd5de","tid":801954,"uid":37863,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"呢D全部都係表面野，有冇人入過去做有內幕料爆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828f0cca51d8144c4b4f397cd7c6bd4f43fbe791","tid":801954,"uid":37863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31d58d75901e51f7ae4482921f20447d2e08bf5a","tid":801954,"uid":35536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:46:11.000Z","msg":"屌 真係好撚仆街<br />\n喺jijis瘋狂開post請人<br />\n但又唔知間公司做乜鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:48:42.000Z","msg":"巴打in過?"},{"pid":"5fceff40e0f721a1ff97863686bfe40ef41c4785","tid":801954,"uid":186208,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"覺得有問題咪米撚做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715ce0164a08f4b6cc06a5bb0868d65c981c769c","tid":801954,"uid":35536,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"828f0cca51d8144c4b4f397cd7c6bd4f43fbe791","tid":801954,"uid":37863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31d58d75901e51f7ae4482921f20447d2e08bf5a","tid":801954,"uid":35536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:46:11.000Z","msg":"屌 真係好撚仆街<br />\n喺jijis瘋狂開post請人<br />\n但又唔知間公司做乜鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:48:42.000Z","msg":"巴打in過?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"冇 睇Job ad加公司網頁都感覺好伏<br />\n乜鳩block chain公司 但又唔覺佢公司做嘅嘢關咩事<br />\n再見到巴打咁好心機起佢底先知原來係咁仆街"},{"pid":"a8d22628674e23a254bf679eeac349752ed